- **Observed result after fix:** All 63 tests pass including the 2 new tests: "preserves unsent text-only final payloads" verifies the fix (unsent text is delivered), and "drops already-sent text-only final payloads" verifies dedup still works. Build succeeds.

- **What was not tested:** Live WhatsApp message delivery — the fix is in the shared `buildReplyPayloads` pipeline used by all channels, not WhatsApp-specific code. The behavior is verified through unit tests with mock pipeline objects that match the real interface contract.
